":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"045b26315ca13de5d20ebfbcef6ed86a3914054c","tid":935423,"uid":120317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34513a804e25aa449f7cde46b5b96fbf972efd68","tid":935423,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T08:53:25.000Z","msg":"孟晚舟透過律師表示，孟晚舟不會違反法庭命令，並願意在保釋期間戴上電子腳鐐。律師更說，孟晚舟有高血壓和<span style=\"color: red;\">睡眠窒息症</span>等健康問題，又表明孟晚舟願意放棄僅有的兩本護照，包括中國護照，和在被捕時遭扣押的香港特區護照。<br />\n<br />\n今次有新嘢玩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T09:00:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T09:37:48.000Z","msg":"睡眠呼吸暫停（英語：sleep apnea或sleep apnoea，又譯作睡眠窒息症或睡眠呼吸暫停）是一種在睡眠期間，暫停呼吸（英語：Apnea）或呼吸減弱（英語：Hypopnea）症狀導致的睡眠紊亂[1]。每一次的暫停期間可從數秒鐘到數分鐘不等，而且整晚發生好幾次[1]。在一般情況下，這個症狀會產生吵雜的打鼾聲[2]。當重新呼吸時，有時會有窒息或鼻音等的聲音出現[1]。當此症狀破壞正常睡眠時，會造成白天的嗜睡或感到疲累的現象[1]。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hant/睡眠呼吸暂停\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hant%2F%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E6%9A%82%E5%81%9C&d=5rMhux4GCg7QbMmwUwEGI6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=09e6adc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hant/睡眠呼吸暂停</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你扯鼻寒都係病有得保外就醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T12:23:15.000Z","msg":"我量10 次血壓都有一兩次高血壓"},{"pid":"073f339a48e78094ac93fdb062aae179c80c6310","tid":935423,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T12:26:21.000Z","msg":"好過被抑鬱吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfde535b7489afb81cf706feb068a1e652aca031","tid":935423,"uid":48659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T12:29:36.000Z","msg":"無用的，一日中國人死係中國魂<br />\n外交部可以追加幾本比你傍身<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7ab7559235c7b20872d56fac201bafe2fa3a03","tid":